        <abstract> 
<p>Astounded she cares for his book [<hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>] as much as she seems to.</p> 
            <p>Comments on variation among domestic dogs; believes domestic dog has descended from several wild species and those species from a single ancient ancestor.</p> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi> review is unfair.</p> 
            <p>Expects to convert four or five "really good judges".</p>
        </abstract>
